LEVEL GENERATION

Different functions for "marking" tiles with flags, which are then checked to determine final tile type/contents
eg. Function that marks tiles based on a threshold on perlin noise
	and another that marks any tiles surrounding tile with a specific flag
	Can use components and systems for tags and functions of tags and neighbors

Big open circular rooms with pillars and fountains
Corridors and tunnels leading to rooms that break out into great chasms
Real scenic ascii shit